{"tid":1414986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「快入」完全示威手冊","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:02:33.000Z","uid":69696,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"082f768b6183073ca5f5fd62dd9686ca09f82dfa","tid":1414986,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382235/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382235/page/1</a><br />\n之前係上面個post見到本講人群控制既書，有o的諗法想翻譯俾大家睇。<span style=\"color: red;\">請傳俾前線。</span><br />\n<br />\nWarrior crowd control and riot manual <br />\n<a href=\"https://ia800303.us.archive.org/17/items/WarriorCrowdControlRiotManual/warrior_crowd_control.pdf?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=ios_app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fia800303.us.archive.org%2F17%2Fitems%2FWarriorCrowdControlRiotManual%2Fwarrior_crowd_control.pdf%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dios_app&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJCDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=68da8f62\" target=\"_blank\">https://ia800303.us.archive.org/17/items/WarriorCrowdControlRiotManual/warrior_crowd_control.pdf?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=ios_app</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 裝備篇</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATJamem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATJamem.png&h=0fab1f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">所有防具及武器要噴黑</span>。著一樣服裝既人群有展示力量及團結既效果，可以令對方畏懼。 <br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">大圍巾係比口罩好</span>，尤其係<span style=\"color: red;\">浸左醋、蘋果醋或檸檬汁</span>，可以減低TG及pepper spray既效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRXB1e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRXB1e9.jpg&h=db69a76f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&bull; 上身防具可以用<span style=\"color: red;\">運動防具</span>，如越野電單車車手護甲，<span style=\"color: red;\">或捲起及痴實既發泡膠</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjoBgOK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjoBgOK.jpg&h=81f7bf54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/to7RP8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fto7RP8L.jpg&h=9d520fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">前臂防具可用細o的既腳部護甲</span>代替，除左發泡膠之外<span style=\"color: red;\">可用捲起既雜誌</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EdJGff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EdJGff.jpg&h=7883acd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UACZeAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUACZeAr.jpg&h=5bb3f73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 武器篇 </span></ins></strong><br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">顏料彈</span>可以由兩種方法整：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNRWgPj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNRWgPj.png&h=b5a521a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\na. <span style=\"color: red;\">將顏料放係Condom入面，索緊另一端</span>。記得用投擲既方式掟，確保有足夠力道整爆佢。 <br />\nb. <span style=\"color: red;\">係雞蛋頂部吉一個細loan，上下大力chok之後倒晒強汁出黎。蛋乾之後用漏斗倒顏料入去，再用膠紙封口</span>。 <br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">起好路障之後要不停投擲物品，掟空玻璃樽</span>，落地爆開既時候可以嚇對方。 <br />\n&bull; 雞尾酒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Htamf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Htamf6.png&h=a9f67ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n &bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">擲物首要目標係指揮官、槍手、捉人隊伍如速狗隊，<ins>佢地唔會有盾</ins></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/br9kJuD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbr9kJuD.png&h=fb36fe80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2537dd5a718a8670a3b6aefe02991e4bab812feb","tid":1414986,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"其他遲o的再打"},{"pid":"aa9713f15d12065dd6c19eb56ed0b81ae8891167","tid":1414986,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s